title: Volte not working for Etisalat carrier
content: I checked with Etisalat and other similar topics on internet. I don't have much hope from google because others are still waiting for an update from google on unlocking the software for carriers worldwide to enable VOLTE. Anyway posting a thread to see if there is something in future or I should stop buying pixel in future.
